## 12. Use Case Diagram – Online Bill Payment System (Paytm)

### Actors
- User
- Bank
- Admin

### Use Cases
- Register / Login  
- Add Bank Account  
- View Bills  
- Pay Bill  
- Transaction History  

**Flow:**
- User → Login → View Bills → Pay Bill  
- User → Check History  
- Admin → Manage Users  
- Bank → Process Payment  

---

